- This repo is an enterprise GenAI Solution Architecture lab.
- Host is .NET 10 ASP.NET Core + Blazor. APIs under /api/*.
- LLM access is provider-agnostic (OpenAI-style interface).
- Vector store supports Azure AI Search and pgvector (toggle via config).
- Tool calling is allow-listed and validated.
- Agent loop must enforce max steps/time/tokens and be observable.
- Every major decision requires an ADR.